data.title: Wallace, Jessie
data.text:
Hi, my name is Jessie Wallace! I am so excited about beginning my tenth year in education. This will be my 4th year within the COCISD family. I am originally from Natchez, MS. I graduated in 2008 from Mississippi State University with a BS degree and in 2010 from Louisiana State University with a MS degree. Please feel free to contact me with any questions or concerns using my school email jwallace@cocisd.org. I am sincerely looking forward to meeting all of you and making this a great year!

I am teaching Algebra 2, Algebra 2 Honors, and Algebraic Reasoning.

My Schedule for the 2023-2024 school year:

1st period- Algebraic Reasoning

2nd period- Algebra 2

3rd period- Conference

4th period- Algebra 2 (Honors)

5th period- Algebra 2

6th period- Algebra 2

7th period- Algebra 2 (Honors)

8th period- Algebra 2
